race.comment: FOREST PRINCE (1) ran below best last time finishing fifth (31.60) over 516m at Dubbo in a Mix. Comes through a solid form race last start. Rates on top in this line up. TEMORA TERROR (3) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fourth (25.81) from Box 4 at Maitland over 450m. Is yet to taste defeat in two starts from this draw. Worth following up. MAGIC BREAKOUT (4) was in winning form two back (26.04) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 8th. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from six attempts. Key runner on best form. FOR REAL FAITH (2) can run a bold race on best form.
